Korea Zinc to sell 200 , 000 shares . Korea Zinc Co Ltd , a zinc smelter , said on Friday it will sell 200 , 000 of its own common shares to raise working capital . After the sell - off , the company will not hold any of its own shares . The share sale , representing 1 . 16 percent of the company ' s share capital , will take place between October 22 and January 21 , a company statement said . The statement said the shares would be sold on the open market at the previous day ' s closing price . Dongsuh Securities will handle the selloff . Korea Zinc ' s shares closed Friday down 500 won at 18 , 900 . - - Seoul Newsroom ( 822 ) 727 5644 
